1. Mysql Seerver

   Sql
   Setup Mysql server 5.7 as Container stateful with docker

   a. Docker experimenta

      Pull images from docker
      - docker pull <image_name> ; docker pull busybox

      Run Simple Docker 
      - docker run busybox

      List of image in local
      - docker images 

      List of container running
      - docker ps
      - docker ps -a (is exited)

      To deep container
      - docker run -it busybox sh | bash